cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use windroot in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "windroot: observation-driven solar-wind source-region finder"
abstract: >
  windroot fuses magnetic connectivity (PFSS + ballistic back-mapping) with
  spectroscopic outflow evidence (SPICE / Hinode EIS Doppler maps) to identify
  and rank solar-wind source regions on the Sun. Existing tools rely on
  magnetic geometry alone; windroot adds the missing observation-driven
  evidence layer.
authors:
