    email: vibhav.aggarwal2@gmail.com
keywords:
  - solar physics
  - solar wind
  - source regions
  - PFSS
  - ballistic back-mapping
  - magnetic connectivity
  - spectroscopy
  - SPICE
  - Hinode EIS
  - Parker Solar Probe
  - Solar Orbiter
  - PUNCH
